# macOS/iCloud conflict-copy duplicates. This repo lives under ~/Documents
# (iCloud-synced), which spawns "Name 2.swift" / "Name 3.md" conflict copies.
# Duplicate Swift files break `swift build` with redeclaration errors. Ignore
# the whole pattern so they can never be staged; delete them locally when they
# appear (git clean -fdx, or the Finder).
* [0-9].*
* [0-9][0-9].*
